snippet.textDisplay:
Here is the difference between Coke Studio Pakistan and Coke Studio India, 
Coke Studio Pakistan does the voice smooth and very much soothing but Coke Studio India can't do this. We can see in 'Afreen Afreen' the voice of Momina Mustehsan sounds better than this of Kaushiki when we hear and compare listening it in a good headset, but Momina is not even worthy for being compared with the great Kaushiki, but the nervousness of Kaushiki's voice is clear and not even furnished. I can definitely say Kaushiki's live performances are better than this coke studio version. Coke Studio Pakistan is using 100% of what they have, but Coke studio India couldn't use 30% of the gems like Kaushiki and they are just wasting  them. Also Coke studio Bangla is doing better works than Coke Studio India.
